## 📌 About This Project

This project is a **real-time server monitoring dashboard** built using:
- **Grafana** – For visualization and dashboards
- **Prometheus** – For collecting and storing metrics
- **Node Exporter** – For exposing CPU, memory, disk, and network stats
- **Docker Compose** – To run everything with one command

The dashboard shows **live graphs** that auto-refresh every 5 seconds, so anyone can immediately see server health at a glance.

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

| Tool | Version | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| Grafana | Latest | Dashboard & visualization |
| Prometheus | Latest | Metrics collection & storage |
| Node Exporter | Latest | System metrics (CPU, RAM, Disk) |
| Docker | 20.x+ | Containerized deployment |
| Docker Compose | 3.8 | Multi-container orchestration |

